theorem Completion.lift_unique {V W : SemiNormedGroup} [complete_space W] [separated_space W] (f : «expr ⟶ » V W)
    (g : «expr ⟶ » (Completion.obj V) W) : «expr ≫ » Completion.incl g = f → g = Completion.lift f := fun h =>
  (normed_add_group_hom.extension_unique _ fun v => ((ext_iff.1 h) v).symm).symm
#align Completion.lift_unique Completion.lift_unique
